Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(287.16,122.14)}她只是要找個地方住
