Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.56,0:44:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(238.2,38.7)}床單下的安德伍德夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.56,0:44:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(235.2,179.1)}和攝影師\N亞當·嘉樂威\N的私情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊芙琳\NEvelyn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-丹頓先生  -叫我雷米就行\N- Mr. Danton. - Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你最近怎樣  -我還行  挺不錯\N- How are you? - I'm OK. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好久不見  -是啊  有段時間了\N- Been awhile. - Yeah, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-早上好  -副總統先生\N- Good morning. - Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷特豪爾酋長\NChief Whitehall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德魯·傑克遜也要來嗎\NIs Andrew Jackson going to be joining us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美國第七任總統  曾在1812年戰爭中與印第安人血戰  得號"印第安人殺手"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  這是嚴重的疏忽\NNo, I'm sorry, that's a terrible oversight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  麻煩你  把畫像拿走\NDoug, will you... remove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們先照相吧\NWhy don't we take the photograph first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位請坐\NPlease have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們談談聯邦認證吧\NLet's talk federal recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必貴部落已經等待許久了\NYour tribe has waited long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哪位  -是我  麗薩\N- Who is it? - It's me. It's Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能進去嗎\NCan I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要做些臨時工\NTemp jobs, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文職工作\NClerical work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼下我在一個牙醫診所兼職\NRight now I'm doing part-time at a dentist's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接待員\NReception.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大材小用\NYou deserve better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就只能將就了\NIt is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都好久沒進星巴克了\NThis is the first time I've had Starbucks since I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今這對我而言是種奢侈了\NIt's a luxury for me these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許格蘭頓-希爾能提供你一個職位\NMaybe there's something for you at Glendon Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你了\NThat's nice of you to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只怕那樣的公司我做不來\Nbut I'm not the right fit for a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當然能\NSure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在非盈利領域工作20年\NTwenty years' experience in the non-profit sphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也經常和非政府組織協作\Nwe coordinated all the time NGOs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的經驗對我們會很有價值\Nyou'd be a valuable asset to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-克萊爾當初就不該解雇你  -可不是\N- Claire should've never let you go. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不說了\NWell... I'll hold my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和她現在也不聯繫了\NShe and I don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們鬧僵了\NWe had a falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她不是個忠誠的人  -的確不是\N- Loyalty isn't her thing. - No, it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看她不會忠於任何人\NI don't think she's loyal to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-也許除了她丈夫吧  -也許吧  也難說\N- Except maybe her husband. - Maybe... maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不確定  但是\NNothing I know for certain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和一個人共事那麼久...\N...spend a decade working for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她威脅你了嗎\NShe threaten you or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  她只是不肯走\NNo. She just wouldn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不想報警\NIt's not like I wanted to call the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也不是壞人\NShe's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是...\NNo, no, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試著和她談  但她又開始抽了\NI tried to talk to her. Then she lit up a pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-冰毒  -是的\N- Meth? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們做室友時整天吸那個\NWhen we were roommates that's all it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經難以自拔\NI used to be really deep into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有海洛因\NHeroin, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到我加入了團契\NAnd then I found the fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能幫你什麼\NWhat can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  我不該\NI'm sorry. I shouldn't --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很高興你來找我\NNo, I'm glad you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你上班要遲到了\NI know you're late for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就請病假\NI'll call in sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  我沒事  我這就走\NDon't do that. It's fine. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別走\NStay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說  別回去\NI mean, don't go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行嗎\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你鑰匙  方便你進出\NKeys. In case you need to come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大約七點半回來\NI'll be back around 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用不著謝我\NYou don't have to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只要總統一個電話\NAll the President has to do is pick up the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大橋就能批下來了\Nand the bridge is approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果總統想參與這事\NIf the President had wanted to be involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他早就打電話了\Nhe would have already made that call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是他的提議  琳達\NIt's his initiative, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是  但現在貿易戰已經打響了\NWas his initiative. We're in a trade war now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也用不著把好端端的政策全丟掉\NBut that doesn't mean we have to abandon good policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會與他現在的立場不一致\NIt's inconsistent with his current stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外資投資管理委員會有30天的時間批准開建\NThe Committee on Foreign Investment has 30 days to approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在只剩六天了\NThere's only six days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有美國總統的直接指示\NThey won't act without a directive from the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會批准的\NPresident of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  你一直堅定支持對中國\NI'm confused, you've been the biggest proponent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採取強硬態度\Nof a strong position against China.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話可不對\NThat is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早先的建議與此相反\NI advocated the opposite early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎很在乎這座橋\NYou seem fixated on this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的原因嗎\NIs something else going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失業率達到9.2%\NUnemployment is at nine-point-two,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通貨膨脹率飆升\Ninflation is skyrocketing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就要丟掉多數席位了\Nwe're on the verge of losing our majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統需要一則好消息向世人公佈\NThe president needs to offer a piece of good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一座橋  簡直是微不足道\NA bridge? That's a drop in the bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作  基礎設施\NJobs, infrastructure,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,削減赤字\Ndeficit reduction--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是沒說實話\NYou're still not being straight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒別的用心\NI have no ulterior motive here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可如果你非要這麼想\Nbut if you feel that strongly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統也非要這麼想的話\Nand the president feels that strongly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不管了\Nthen I'll back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會再提了\NI won't mention it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個明智的決定\NI think that's a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們該團結起來\NWe should be a united front.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常贊同\NI couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼凡事都這麼不容易\NWhy does everything have to be a struggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒人能說一次"好"嗎\NCan't some people just say "Yes" for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要總統明後天的日程表\NI need the president's schedule for the next two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她改變主意了嗎\NShe change her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得呢\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們下一步做什麼\NSo what's our next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去辦橋的事\NI'll focus on the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去跟印第安人事務部談\Nyou talk to the Indian affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷特豪爾的部落越早得到認證\NThe sooner that Whitehall's tribe gets recognized,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭場就能越早動工\Nthe sooner they can break ground on that casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\NYes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許這對我有幫助\NMaybe it will help me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多公開談談那事\NIf I talk about it more in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像在你的訪談上那樣\NI mean that's what your interview did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打進電話  公開說出那些事\NWhen I called. When I could say those things out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想讓你覺得你有義務如此\NWell, we don't want you to feel obligated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道媒體還一直纏著你\NI know the press hasn't left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們還要繼續給我拍照\NIf they're going to keep taking pictures of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至少該說點什麼\NI should at least say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥金尼斯上軍事法庭指日可待\NWell, that's only going to become more intense
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事態會越來越緊張\Nwhen McGinnis gets closer to his court-marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我知道\NYeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我準備好了\NI'm prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能去跟軍事委員會談談\NIf you come and speak to the Armed Services Committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出你的往事\Ntell your story,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼法案一定能進入投票階段\NI feel confident we can get it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的重磅新聞他們不能無視\NI'd be too much coverage to ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得法案會通過嗎\NAnd you think it will pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要先通過委員會\NWe need to get it through committee first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要說明  梅根\NBut let's be clear, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不光要舉證\Nit's not just the testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍後你還得面對媒體\NWe'll need you to do a media avail after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍照片  做聲明\NPhoto ops, a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -你不是一個人\N- Ok. - You won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直支持你\NI'll be standing right next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我\NAnd so will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這樣做對嗎\NDo you think we're doing the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她拉到鏡頭前\NHauling her in front of the cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說她想這樣做  我們得相信她\NWe have to trust her when she says she wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但重要的是\NBut it's very important
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是你  白宮也支持我們\Nthat the White House backs us up on this, not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定加勒特會不會公開表示支持\NI'm not sure if Garrett will get involved publicly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能和他談談嗎\NWell, can you talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們最近沒怎麼交談\NWe haven't been doing much talking about anything lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況還沒好轉嗎\NThings haven't gotten any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們差不多一個禮拜沒說過話了\NWe haven't said a word to each other in almost a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也經歷過  真可怕\NI've been there, it's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和弗蘭克嗎\NWith Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是怎麼做的\NWhat did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們找了一個人\NWe saw someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指心理咨詢師嗎\NYou mean a therapist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不擔心被曝光嗎\NWeren't you worried about exposure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個牧師\NHe was a minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格說  他不是心理咨詢師\NHe wasn't exactly a therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更像是精神指引那種的\NIt was more like a spiritual guidance, type thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的區別是他有學位\NThe only difference was that he had a degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以幫你聯繫\NI could put you in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太冒險了\NIt's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個建議而已\NJust a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是改變主意就告訴我\NLet me know if you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你能試著和加勒特談談嗎\NIn the meantime, can you try to talk to Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們非常需要他的支持\NWe really need his support with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請帶他進來\NShow him in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米\NRemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼正式\NSo formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐吧\NWould you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不該讓實習生工作到這麼晚\NShouldn't keep your interns so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許沒有個人生活  但他們有\NYou and I might not have lives, but they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有工作沒做完就要繼續做  這他們懂\NWhen there's work to be done, we work. They know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼晚上10點叫我過來\NWhy am I here at 10 at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨的錢從哪來的\NWhere is the GOP getting their money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是問那兩千五百萬吧\NThat is a $25 million question, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定知道\NYou must have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會那麼認為\NWhat makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你無所不知\NBecause you know things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以格蘭頓-希爾升你做合夥人\NThat's why Glendon Hill made you partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們大部分客戶都是民主黨人\NMost of our clients are Democrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一樣毫不知情\NI'm just as much in the dark as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要失去我的選區了  雷米\NI'm losing in my district, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我能幫你\NAnd I wish I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我贏得選舉  也無所謂了\NEven if I pull off a win, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨佔據眾議院多數席位\NThe GOP takes the House,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會被踢出領導層\NI lose my spot in the leadership,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去職務  失去我為之努力的一切\Nthis office, everything I've worked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我替你難過\NI feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你想要的是我不知道的信息\NBut you want information I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們上次的見面\NAre you upset
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你不高興了嗎\Nabout the last time we saw each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有\NNot at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的很清楚\NI made myself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能談談嗎\NCan we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不談工作  不談政治\NNo work, no politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想談什麼都可以\NWe can talk about whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟人約會  從未超過六個月\NI've never... been with anyone for more than six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在軍隊的時候  總是四處奔波\NWhen I was in the army I was always on the move and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入國會之後\NSince I've been in Congress,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又實在沒有時間\NI just haven't had time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要你嫁給我\NI wasn't asking to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想比一夜情更認真一些\NJust to be more than company for a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你依然那麼想嗎\NDo you still want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來了  不是嗎\NI'm here, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們必須劃定一個界限\NThere would have to be clear boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們私底下的事\NWhatever we have privately
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能影響我們的公事關係\Ncouldn't affect our professional relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就不該在你的辦公室談這些\NThen we shouldn't be having this conversation in your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興我們能把話說開\NI'm glad we had this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還想見我  給我打電話\NIf you'd like to have another, just call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以省掉秘書這一關\NWe can leave the secretaries out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再看看  讓琳達聯繫你們\NI'll review this and have Linda get in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝  先生  -謝謝  先生\N- Thank you, sir. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  總統先生\NGood morning, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  弗蘭克\NHi, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把波本威士忌放在家裏了\NI left my bourbon at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但您有時間喝個咖啡嗎\Nbut you have time for some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用  你自便\NI'm fine, you go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟您談談傑斐遜港大橋\NI wanted to talk to you about the Port Jefferson Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達說你們倆談過了\NLinda told me you two spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您重新考慮過嗎\NHave you reconsidered?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在時機不對  弗蘭克\NIt's not the right time, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到緊張局勢過去後\NWe'll find some other project
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再找別的項目展示我們的計劃\Nto showcase our program once tensions subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在競選中\NDuring the campaign,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您反覆承諾會重視重要的基建\Nyou repeatedly promised to address critical infrastructure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經進入了您任期的第二個年頭\NWe're well into your second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個項目已經蓄勢待發\NThis project is ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您也不想再重頭搞一個吧\Nyou don't want to have to start from square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在考慮中期選舉的事\NI'm thinking midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得表現出一致性\NWe have to project consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但人們不會為了一致性投票\NExcept people don't vote for consistency,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們只為確實的進展投票\Nthey vote for concrete progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達說你似乎對這座橋很執迷\NLinda mentioned that you seemed obsessed with this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在覺得她說對了\NI'm beginning to think she was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個背後捅刀的噁心婊子\NThe backstabbing, vomit-inducing bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說對了嗎  弗蘭克\NIs she right, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說你為什麼這麼在乎這座橋\NTell me why this bridge is so important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想把您捲進來\NI wanted to insulate you from this--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\NFrom what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您讓我與中國人私下接觸\NYou asked me to back channel with the Chinese
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就繼續那麼做了\Nand I have continued to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我讓你停止跟中國人私下接觸\NNo, I told you to stop back channeling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你還是那麼做了嗎\Nand you did anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不告訴我  弗蘭克\NWithout informing me, Frank--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得拉開您的距離\NI needed to distance you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事是不能讓總統知道的\NThere are issues that a president cannot be aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事\NWhat issues--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我能告訴您的是\NBut, what I can tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大橋的建設\N...is that the building of this bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以直接影響我們在中期選舉中\Ndirectly affects our ability to combat the Republicans
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與共和黨的對抗\Nin the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國人是不是...\NHave the Chinese--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  您正在問\NMr. President, you are asking questions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不想知道答案的問題\Nyou do not want the answers to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的風險有多大  弗蘭克\NAll right, how much danger are we in, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們現在就結束談話  就沒有風險\NNone if we end this conversation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我覺得\NSometimes I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經無法控制我自己的政府了\NI'm losing control over my goddamn administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您承受著很大壓力  先生\NYou're under pressure, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但您並沒有失控\Nbut you're not losing control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人在幫您\NYou have people who are looking out for you:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  琳達  您妻子\Nme, Linda, your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對她也快失去控制了\NI might be losing control of her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該這麼說\NI shouldn't have said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然她也是為我著想\NOf course she wants the best for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾說了什麼嗎\NHas Claire said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她們有聊天\NI know they talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不多\NNot much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是說你們之間有點磕磕絆絆\Njust that things have been a little rocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是說得太輕了\NWell, that's an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的工作是世界上最難做的\NYou have the most difficult job on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換了誰婚姻上都會出現問題\NIt would take a toll on any marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我勸您\NWhich is why I'm urging you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新考慮一下橋的事\Nto reconsider your decision on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這話不是以副總統的身份\NAnd I'd say that not as your vice president...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是以你朋友的身份\Nbut as your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我在乎你\NBecause I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我會再看看\NAll right, I'll... I'll have another look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您  總...\NThank you, Mr--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  加勒特\NThank you, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗羅斯特先生\NMr. Frost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早\NMorning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們2006年就提交了所有文件\NWe filed all our paperwork back in 2006.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事無鉅細  該做得都做了\NWe dotted all of our I's and crossed all of our T's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有超過317份申請\NThere's over 317 applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一份申請最少需要一年去評估\NEach one requires at least a year to review.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你需要多雇些調查員  -不只是人事的問題\N- You need more researchers. - It's not just personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要考慮出行  歸檔  行政工作\NThere's travel, filing, administration...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出個價吧\NName the figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一千二  三百萬\NTwelve, thirteen million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這需要國會的撥款\NThat requires an appropriation from Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統會搞定的\NThe vice president can make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但首先你得認證尤干亞部落\NBut first we need you to recognize the Ugaya tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們規定  要分先來後到\NOur policy is first come, first serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的申請我們\NThere are other applications which we--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼爾·拉尼根把我們踢出部落了\NDaniel Lanagin disenrolled us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們失去了印第安人事務局的福利\NWe lost our right to BIA benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不單只是要開賭場吧\NIs this more about starting a casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了討回公道\NIt's about correcting an injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能牽扯到部落糾紛中\NI can't be getting involved in inner-tribal conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以\NYes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要那筆撥款\NIf you want that appropriation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月\NTwo months.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果歷史核查沒問題  或許能更短\NMaybe less if all the ancestry holds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根知道了\NLanagin knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼說\NAnd what did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想見面\NHe wants to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這次是去他的地盤\NBut on his turf this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想個法子  讓我能去密蘇里\NI need a way to get to Missouri
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不引人注意\Nwithout attracting any attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏麥克的選區在堪薩斯城\NWomack's district's in Kansas City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離賭場不遠\NIt's not far from the casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他最近有什麼活動\NSee if he has any events coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集會  籌款之類的\NRallies, fundraisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾法案的聯署人找得怎麼樣了\NHow's it coming with co-sponsors for Claire's bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好  進展很大\NTerrific. We're making great progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一篇演講  讓國會明白\NOne speech. It'll send a message to Congress that --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也讓參謀長聯席會議知道我要踐踏他們...\NAnd a message to the Joint Chiefs that I'm trampling on--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年有兩萬四千起性侵事件\NTwenty-four thousand assaults last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有三千起上報\Nonly 3,000 reported because--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是什麼情況\NI know the figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多少人因為創傷而自殺\NDo you know how many suicides result from the trauma--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是數據的問題\NIt's not the question of statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部法案能挽救生命\NThis bill will save lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能晚點再說嗎\NCan we discuss this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次會面還是我預約的呢  加勒特\NI had to schedule this meeting, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在大中午的  特莉莎\NIt's the middle of the day, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你十分清楚\NYou know very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逼我回家再遊說你\NDon't make me lobby you when I go home--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打擾了  總統先生\NI'm sorry to interrupt, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘書長到了\NThe secretary general's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再給我兩分鐘\NI got two more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在12點30了  他約的是12點15\NIt's 12:30. He was scheduled for 12:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上走\NI'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該挽留我\NYou were supposed to tell me to stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很高興我至少還值兩分鐘\Nbut it's nice to know I'm worth at least two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  特莉莎\NHi, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事的\NNo, please, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太糟了\NOh, that's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  當然\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找找他的電話\NLet me grab his number for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫托馬斯·拉金醫生\NHis name is Dr. Thomas Larkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,號碼是2022516258\Nat 202-251-6258.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想的話  我可以提前和他聯繫\NAnd if you'd like, I can give him a call beforehand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他知道你要去找他\Nand let him know you'll be reaching out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  有什麼我能幫忙的儘管開口\NOkay. Well you let me know if I can be of any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  特莉莎\NGood night, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧\NWe'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的主旨是將色原說\NThe idea is to take color theory
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徹底顛覆\Nand turn it on its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打破所有陳規\NBreak all the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是精彩\NThey're gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你的客戶是誰來著\NWho'd you say your client is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說過\NI didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想沒準我認識他\NI was just wondering if maybe I knew them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識\NYou don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫且說他是個\NLet's say he's a collector
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四處發掘新人才的收藏家吧\Nalways on the lookout for new talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為亞當·嘉樂威工作  對嗎\NI understand you work for Adam Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能掙些生活費\Nit's a way to pay the bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你喜歡那種風格\NI mean, Adam's a good photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當的確是個優秀的攝影師\Nif you like that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我則對形態更感興趣\NI'm much more interested in form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些加起來多少錢\NHow much for all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全買了\NI'd like to buy them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密蘇里州的"不輕信州"外號可不是白叫的\NMissouri is the Show Me State for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正要向全國人民證明\NAnd we need to show the rest of America
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的領導層堅實可靠\Nthat we can keep our leadership intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見滿屋賓朋\NIt is a pleasure to look out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人人喜笑顏開  我很高興\Nand see a room full of smiling faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場面在華盛頓特區可不是天天都能見到\NThat's not something you see every day in Washington, D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的編輯怎麼說\NWhat did your editors say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五千字\N5,000 words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起碼應該翻倍啊\NThis should be twice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能爭取到八千字\NI can probably get them to eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我還要採訪第一夫人\Nbut I'm gonna need the first lady, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單獨採訪\NSeparate interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我和安德伍德先生商量一下\NLet me talk to Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是你而不是康納來和我談這事\NHow come you're coming to me with this instead of Connor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別跟別人說  他辭職了\NBetween you and me, he's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳槽去太空探索技術公司了\NHe got a job at SpaceX.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自願的還是被人逼走的\NHis choice or was he pushed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人不喜歡和我共事  馬特\NPeople don't like working with me, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大約是絕無僅有的一個\NYou may be the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜歡和你打交道\NI don't like you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果能採訪到第一夫人  我或許會喜歡你\NI might if you give me the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們明天要跟軍事委員會面談\NThey'll both be speaking to armed services tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有梅根·漢納希\NAlong with Megan Hennessy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那個被將軍...\NShe's the one the general--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給你安排單獨專訪  短信溝通你的報道\NI'll set up a one-on-one, text you for your piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  等你消息了  老兄\NAll right, let me know, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意為《時代》效勞  夥計\NAnything for the Times, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意為《時代》效勞  是吧\NAnything for the Times, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻把我們擋在捐助者會議大門外\NThen we get shut out of donor meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是雜誌  沒錯\NThe magazine. And yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德·塔斯克\NRaymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老闆去年十月去見過他\NYour boss went to see him last October.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都記在國會的旅行報告裏了\NIt's in his congressional travel report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我還沒來工作\NBefore my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說他們倆從沒見過\NYou said they didn't communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的原話是"據我瞭解不認識"\NI said, "Not to my knowledge."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在就在密蘇里\NWe're in Missouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是捐助者之一\NHe's not one of the donors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能引述你的話嗎\NI can quote you on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別把我的名字拼錯了\NIf you spell my name right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般來講  我不引述北方作家的話\NNow, normally, I don't quote Northern writers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有時候他們中也有人\Nbut every now and then one of them
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能說出挺有道理的話\Nsays something that makes a lot of sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位叫愛默生的老兄  你們沒準聽說過\Nand this Emerson fellow you probably heard of,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾經說  交友的唯一辦法\Nonce wrote that the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是自己夠朋友\Nto have a friend is to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想各位非常清楚\NI think you all know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰瑞對他的選區人民有多夠朋友\Nwhat kind of a friend Terry has been to this district.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天  我驕傲地向各位介紹他\NSo I am proud to introduce him today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並稱他為我的朋友\Nand to call him my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有請多數黨領袖\NWould you please welcome, the majority leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰瑞·烏麥克議員\NRepresentative Terry Womack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  副總統先生\NThank you, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都安排好了\NWe all set?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴媒體\NI told the press
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你將和幾位捐助者私下會面\Nyou were having some private meetings with contributors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人質疑嗎\NAny protests?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  除了艾拉·薩伊德\NWe're good except for Ayala Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝  -謝謝  她怎麼了\N- Thank you. - Thank you. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是個盲點\NPotential blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去車那邊  邊走邊說\NTell me on the way to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\NMr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許亂叫\NCalm down. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎\NWelcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是愉快的巧遇啊  雷蒙德\NWhat a pleasant surprise, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\NMr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為今天要和你單獨見面呢  丹尼爾\NI was expecting to see you privately today, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事關重大\NIt's a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把"酋長"都請來了\NI invite all the chiefs to the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泳池不錯\NNice pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒在裏面游過\NI've never swum in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氯水弄得我眼睛疼\NThe chlorine hurts my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想游的話  歡迎試水\NYou're welcome to take a dip in it if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧\NAnother time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德跟我說你喜歡吃肋排\NWell, Raymond tells me you're a ribs man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒有三份頂級的肉\NWell, I've got three of the choicest pieces of meat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這輩子難得一嘗\Nyou'll ever see in your life coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對不會想錯過\NYou do not want to pass on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會待很久\NI won't be here long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,言歸正傳  尤干亞群體\NSo, the Ugaya band.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰山一角\NTip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不是正式的部落\NThey're not a real tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就要成為正式的了\NThey're about to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  他們是一群製造麻煩的傢伙\NNo, they're a bunch of troublemakers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是報太大希望\Nwith too much hope on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他們得到認證\NOnce they get recognized,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能建立自己的賭場\Nthey're gonna have their own casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最快也要兩年吧\NIn two years... at best?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著還有泳池好好享受吧\NYou better enjoy this pool while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.13,0:23:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你的賭場\NI don't think your casino
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承受不住那麼激烈的競爭\Ncan stand that sort of competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為懷特豪爾一離開印第安人事務局\NWho do you think Whitehall called
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最先給誰打了電話\Nas soon as he left the BIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你承諾兩年後給他們賭場\NYou offer them a casino two years from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們能給出他真正想要的\Nwe offered what they really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回歸我的部落\NReenrollment in my tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的冰山一角正在融化  弗蘭克\NA tip of your iceberg is melting, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你時間也不多了\NAnd you do not have time on your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何\Nso how about this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我和加勒特重歸於好\NYou help me repair my relationship with Garrett,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.99,0:24:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹和我就讓資金\NDan and I here get the money
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流向正確的方向\Nflowing back in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.45,0:24:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何\NHow about this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.50,0:24:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓印第安人事務局調查你們兩個\NI get the BIA to investigate both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和馮的關係  洗錢\NConnection to Feng, laundering--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以  但你不會\NYou could, but you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.13,0:24:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不敢\NYou don't dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經資助民主黨九年了\NMy money has been going to the Democrats for nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.77,0:24:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是他們的黨鞭\NYou were the whip for all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.29,0:24:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我們扯進來  你也自身難保\NYou implicate us, you implicate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會殃及領導層的每個人\NAnd everyone in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛排來了\NHere comes the steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.19,0:24:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會喜歡這個的  弗蘭克\NNow you are going to enjoy this, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.67,0:24:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.36,0:24:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.81,0:24:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗吧  弗蘭克\NNow dig in, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.67,0:24:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別喂蒼蠅了\NBefore the flies get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了  謝謝\NI'll pass, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.83,0:24:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是醬燒松阪牛肉\NThis is soy-fed Matsusaka beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.75,0:24:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道  我的祖先會對這頭牛禱告\NYou know, my ancestors would've prayed to this heifer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.42,0:24:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祭奠它的靈魂\Nto honor her spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:24:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是兩百塊一磅\NBut at 200 bucks a pound,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.32,0:24:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想  傳統還是滾邊吧\NI figure... fuck tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.56,0:25:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  及時行樂  弗蘭克\NCome on, live a little, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要叫副總統先生\NMr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.55,0:25:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的副總統\NNot my Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.57,0:25:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在是在保留地的地盤上\NYou're on sovereign land.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.02,0:25:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗可真好猜  不是嗎\NDogs are so predictable, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.86,0:25:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我安排與沃克會面\NSet up a meeting with Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.06,0:25:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以就今晚  我六點能到\NTonight, if possible. I should be back by six.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.26,0:25:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根沒讓步嗎\NLanagin didn't budge?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.46,0:25:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓尤干亞回歸了  得馬上把橋的事敲定\NHe reenrolled the Ugaya. We have to get the bridge approved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.08,0:25:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去聯繫琳達\NI'll call Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.89,0:25:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繞開她  我不想讓她參與會面\NBypass her, I don't want her in the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.85,0:25:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就去辦\NI'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.80,0:25:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.55,0:25:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密查姆  和飛機聯繫\NMeechum, get in touch with the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.73,0:25:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回程航班要做肋排\Nhave them make ribs for the flight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.89,0:25:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\NYes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.81,0:27:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生  有空嗎\NMr. Vice President, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.28,0:27:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  總統要見我\NI'm sorry, the President asked to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.61,0:27:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  他沒有  是你要求會面\NNo, he didn't, you requested the meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.17,0:27:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我取消了\Nand I took it off the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.73,0:27:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹了什麼\NYou did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.81,0:27:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你辦公室聊\NLet's go in your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.96,0:27:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你撒謊了  弗蘭克\NYou lied, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.01,0:27:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說橋的事你不管了\NYou said you would let the bridge go
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.17,0:27:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就背著我搗鬼\Nand then you went behind my back,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.19,0:27:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這會兒就想這麼做\Njust like you're trying to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.00,0:27:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要徵求你的同意\NI do not require your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.74,0:27:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  但你應該叫上我\NNo, but you should involve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.51,0:27:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統和副總統之間\NThe President and the Vice President
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.82,0:27:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題需要私下討論\Nhave issues they must discuss privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.77,0:27:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對我保密\NWhen you are secretive,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.63,0:27:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就做不好我的工作\Nit prevents me from being able to do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣把會面取消\NAnd when you cancel meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.88,0:27:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我做不好我的工作\Nit prevents me from being able to do mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.06,0:27:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想聊聊\NWhich is why I wanted to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.05,0:27:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才能解決問題\Nso we can work things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.13,0:27:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不想浪費時間  -我們應該合作\N- I will not waste my time - We should be working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.44,0:27:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膨脹你的自尊心\Ninflating your sense of self-importance!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.34,0:27:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.30,0:27:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你贏過多少次選舉\NHow many elections have you won?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.53,0:28:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當過多少個國會委員會的主席\NHow many congressional committees have you chaired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.83,0:28:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我在競選時推薦了你\NWould you even be working in the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.14,0:28:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在會在白宮工作嗎\Nif I hadn't recommended you during the campaign?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.14,0:28:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一直在還你人情嗎\NI returned that favor and then some.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.11,0:28:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的辦公桌在哪\NLook where your desk is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.77,0:28:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就互不相欠了\NAnd I'd say we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.40,0:28:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要還想讓我尊重你\NAnd if you want to maintain my respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.35,0:28:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的做法大錯特錯\Nyou're going about it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.71,0:28:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想跟你解決問題\NI asked you in here to work out a situation--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.09,0:28:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是強行要求\NYou didn't ask, you demanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.62,0:28:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不允許自己被排除在外\NI will not be left out of the loop,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.46,0:28:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是總統的幕僚長\NI'm the president's chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.19,0:28:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼當幕僚長嗎\NYou call this being chief of staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.28,0:28:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,篡改他的日程安排\NMicromanaging his datebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.60,0:28:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是高級排程員\NI'd say that's more of a glorified scheduler.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.99,0:28:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有我盡職盡責  白宮會無法正常運作\NThe White House would fall off its rails without me doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.89,0:28:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你確定嗎  -我確定\N- Are you certain about that? - Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.85,0:28:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我時刻為總統著想\NI look out for the president 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.31,0:28:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他知曉一切\NI keep him informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.51,0:28:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫他理清輕重緩急\NI keep his priorities straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.19,0:28:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當副總統前一切都好好的  弗蘭克\NWe did just fine before you became vice president, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.53,0:28:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們現在就去總統辦公室\NAll right, let's go over to the Oval Office right now
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.99,0:28:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓總統做個選擇\Nand ask the president to choose:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是幕僚長還是副總統\Nhis chief of staff or his vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.74,0:28:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他會選誰\NI know what the answer would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.28,0:28:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要一起去嗎\NYou wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.68,0:28:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你也不敢\NI didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.51,0:28:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明早要見到總統\NNow I will see the president tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.03,0:28:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管有沒有安排\Nschedule or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.22,0:28:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開前請把燈關上\NAnd please, turn out the lights before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.23,0:29:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你回家了\NI thought you went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.00,0:29:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有\NNo, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.18,0:29:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您有空嗎\NUm, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.69,0:29:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎\NIs there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.84,0:29:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道您在重新考慮建橋的事  我想\NI know you are reconsidering the bridge project and I want-
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.64,0:29:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在審查  我很快會決定的\NI'm reviewing it. I'll make my decision soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.68,0:29:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您已經做過決定了  先生\NBut you already made a decision, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.06,0:29:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心這事您是想多了\NI'm concerned that you are overthinking this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-如果我們出爾反爾  -我沒說明白嗎\N- If we backtrack... - Did I not make myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.68,0:29:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想表達我的看法  先生\NI'm just trying to offer my advice, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.02,0:29:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經瞭解了\NWhich I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.80,0:29:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不用再聽第二遍了\NAnd which I don't need to hear again
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.86,0:29:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  謝謝\Nbut... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.82,0:29:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道副總統昨天和您談過\NI know the vice president spoke to you yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.94,0:29:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-平心而論  -你知道我重視你的想法  琳達\N- and in fairness... - You know I value your input, linda,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.08,0:29:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說我已經瞭解了\Nbut when I say I've heard it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.26,0:29:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是真的瞭解了\Nyou need to know I mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.66,0:29:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  先生\NOf course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.25,0:29:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的事嗎\NIs there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.22,0:29:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了  先生\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.85,0:29:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-晚安  -晚安\N- Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.66,0:29:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我失望了\NYou disappointed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.52,0:30:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了我需要時間\NI told you it would take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.23,0:30:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有線索嗎\NAny leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.89,0:30:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在查他當州參議員時的事\NI've been going over his state senate days.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.77,0:30:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這沒法快\NIt's a slow process.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.32,0:30:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得徹底排查\NI have to be thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.84,0:30:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼我兩天找到的\NSo how is it that i've found more in two days
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.55,0:30:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你兩個月查到的還多\Nthan you have in two months?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.41,0:30:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.60,0:30:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還得替你完成差事\NI've had to do your job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.19,0:30:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有發現嗎\NYou found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.34,0:30:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我來問你這個問題\NI'm the one who's supposed to ask that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.39,0:30:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了什麼\NWhat'd you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.39,0:30:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定能幫忙\NMaybe I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.78,0:30:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在給弗蘭克幹活兒嗎\NAre you working for Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.96,0:30:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我是他的媒體主管\NYeah, as his communications director.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.69,0:30:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是問你在幫他收集情報嗎\NNo, are you working for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.29,0:30:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.76,0:30:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給的錢比他能給的要多得多\NHe couldn't pay me a fraction of what you're offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.76,0:30:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別騙我了\NDon't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.91,0:30:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你對我的能力沒信心了\NLook, if you've lost confidence in my ability--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.82,0:30:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別他媽再唬我了\NStop fucking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.16,0:30:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的選擇是錯的  賽斯\NYou made the wrong choice, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.38,0:30:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.39,0:30:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼也不是\NYou're nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.99,0:30:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是只寄生蟲\NYou're a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.22,0:30:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一樣  丹頓\NSo are you Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.04,0:30:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過更人模狗樣一點\NJust in a nicer suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.29,0:31:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道可能是什麼嗎\NDo you know what it might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.30,0:31:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意打聽\NWell, keep your ear to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.84,0:31:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是賽斯\NThat was Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.92,0:31:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他覺得雷米可能找到了我們的把柄\NHe thinks Remy may have something on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.54,0:31:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.04,0:31:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道\NHe doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.21,0:31:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你覺得可不可能是...  -不\N- Do you think it could be-- - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.59,0:31:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算有  也肯定是無關痛癢的小事\NIf it's anything I'm sure it's innocuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.89,0:31:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們撐得住\NNothing we can't weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.38,0:31:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我猜  他們是在虛張聲勢\NBut my bet is they're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.55,0:31:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過想嚇唬我們\NJust to make us paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.55,0:31:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他是個危險的人  不是嗎  我是說雷蒙德\NBut he's a dangerous man, isn't he? Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.80,0:31:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也可以很危險\NWe can be dangerous too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.16,0:31:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果情勢需要\NWhen we need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.77,0:31:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*主啊  情不自禁*\N*Lord, I just can't*
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.77,0:32:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*偶爾灑淚*\N*keep from crying sometimes.*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.55,0:32:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*主啊  情不自禁*\N*Lord, I just can't*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.60,0:32:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*偶爾灑淚*\N*keep from crying sometimes.*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.76,0:32:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*世界充滿哀傷*\N*When the world's filled with sorrow*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.45,0:32:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*而我飽含熱淚*\N*and my eyes are filled with tears.*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.61,0:32:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*主啊  情不自禁*\N*Lord, I just can't*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.11,0:32:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*偶爾灑淚*\N*keep from crying sometimes.*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.04,0:32:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別停\NDon't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.54,0:32:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經當過應召女郎\NI used to be a call girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.46,0:32:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要逃離那種生活\NI had to get away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.12,0:32:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才來這裏\NAnd that's why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.53,0:33:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於我  你還有很多不知道\NThere's a lot of stuff you don't know about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.24,0:33:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想說  就什麼都不用說\NYou don't have to say anything you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.46,0:33:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在公交車上拍我肩膀的時候\NWhen you tapped on my shoulder on the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.41,0:33:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一種感覺...\Nthere was something...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.10,0:33:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛\NYour eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.97,0:33:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這麼說真是太蠢了  -不\N- That sounds really, really dumb. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.16,0:33:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道怎麼說\NUm, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.86,0:33:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想把一切都告訴你\NI felt like I wanted to tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.07,0:33:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我能信任你\NLike, that I could trust you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.01,0:33:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-儘管與你素昧平生  -你可以信任我的\N- even though I didn't know you. - You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.91,0:33:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒信任過任何人\NI never trusted anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.30,0:33:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愛過別人嗎\NHave you ever loved anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.61,0:34:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.36,0:34:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這個世界沒什麼期望\NI've never expected much from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.23,0:34:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得它很醜惡\NIt's ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.77,0:34:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是個公平的地方\NIt's not a fair place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.15,0:34:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對我現在擁有的很知足\NI'm happy to have what I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.61,0:34:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興我擁有現在\NI'm glad I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.09,0:34:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都想清楚了\NI've thought it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.02,0:34:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種方式\NAnd there's a way to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.39,0:34:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有曝光的風險\Nso we don't risk any exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.27,0:35:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非要現在聊嗎\NDo we have to talk about this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.06,0:35:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我累了\NI'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.61,0:35:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦袋一團漿糊\NMy brain is f...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.36,0:35:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  現在聊\NYes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.70,0:35:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的婚姻\NBecause it's our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.08,0:35:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要捱過接下來兩年\NIf we're going to survive the next two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.86,0:35:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或六年\Nor six.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.26,0:35:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得做點什麼\NWe need to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.71,0:35:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該互相支持\NWe should be each others' support system.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.42,0:35:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是互相施壓\NNot cause each other stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.39,0:35:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮的基礎不是磚瓦\NThe foundation of this White House is not brick and mortar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.14,0:35:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是我們啊  加勒特\NIt's us, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.73,0:35:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對我很重要\NThis is important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.28,0:35:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你也能重視\NAnd I want it to be important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.78,0:35:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得相信不管你在想什麼辦法\NI have to trust that whatever you're managing,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.84,0:35:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你對我隱瞞了多少\Nto whatever extent you choose not to inform me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.47,0:35:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既不會讓我有危險\Nthat I'm neither at risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.65,0:35:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會讓我被動地縱容明顯的違法行為\Nnor passively condoning something blatantly illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.36,0:35:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有風險都是我一人承擔\NAny risk solely falls on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.60,0:36:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不知情  也不能被指責縱容\Nand you can't be accused of condoning what you're not aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.34,0:36:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知情也一樣糟糕\NBeing not aware is just as egregious.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.20,0:36:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這件事上不是\NNot in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.40,0:36:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在想辦法避開麻煩\NI'm steering the ship away from the rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.07,0:36:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是迎頭撞上\Nnot toward them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.58,0:36:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就給外資投資管理委員會打電話了\NThen I'll call the committee for foreign investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.30,0:36:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的選擇很明智  先生\NYou're making the right decision, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.39,0:36:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有個艱難的決定要做\NI have another difficult decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.95,0:36:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達提交了她的辭職信\NLinda submitted her resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.76,0:36:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很生她的氣\NI was furious with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.47,0:36:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這招讓我很被動\NThat was a very manipulative move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.41,0:36:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能猜到她為什麼這麼做\NI can speculate as to why she made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.60,0:36:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的不滿有道理嗎\NAre her complaints valid?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.40,0:36:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這個問題的看法很主觀\NI have a very biased view on that subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.96,0:36:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聽過她的想法了\NWell, I've heard hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.44,0:36:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說說你的吧\NGive me yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.11,0:36:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達和我時不時會有爭執\NLinda and I don't always agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.20,0:36:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她對您忠心耿耿\NBut she's been very loyal to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.80,0:36:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一名非常得力的幕僚長\Nand a more than competent Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.50,0:36:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我該挽留她嗎\NSo you think I should keep her?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.37,0:36:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她有時會管太寬嗎\NDo I think she oversteps sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.43,0:36:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.37,0:36:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她錯以為自己的意見和我的一樣重要嗎\NDoes she wrongly equate her advice with mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.90,0:36:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事  但是\NOften. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.08,0:36:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想到的問題不在於琳達\Nthe question that occurs to me is not about Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.09,0:37:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算您回絕了她的辭呈\NLet's say you refuse her resignation,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.09,0:37:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消息很有可能傳出去\Nif this gets out, and it could,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.89,0:37:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣所有為您的工作的人  不是都會覺得\Nwon't you be sending a signal to anybody who works for you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.49,0:37:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們可以跟您談判\N...you can be leveraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.98,0:37:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經遞了辭呈\NShe offered her resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.54,0:37:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便留下來心也不在這兒了\NShe's already gone even if she stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.52,0:37:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根  他們準備好了\NMegan. They're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.26,0:37:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  我手一直在抖\NI don't know, my hands are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.82,0:37:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒問題的  梅根\NYou can do this, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.05,0:37:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會在場\NI'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.36,0:37:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有時會恐慌發作\NI get panic attacks sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.42,0:37:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你怕待會兒會發作嗎  -對\N- You're afraid you'll get one? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.57,0:37:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那我們再多等幾分鐘吧\NOK, why don't we ask for a couple more minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.21,0:37:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不成問題  -不是時間的問題\N- that's not a problem. - It's not about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.29,0:37:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐慌說來就來\Nthey just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.21,0:37:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法控制\NI can't control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.53,0:37:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想做了\NI don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.06,0:38:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根  屋裏面有很多\NOK, Megan, there's some of the most senior congressmen
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.09,0:38:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資深國會議員\Nand women in the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.02,0:38:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有媒體  他們專程為你而來\Nand the press, they've shown up just to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.48,0:38:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.33,0:38:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我不想給你施壓\NOK, I don't want to pressure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.26,0:38:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們為了這個策劃了很久\Nbut a lot of planning has gone into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.59,0:38:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別逼我做這個\NPlease don't make me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.30,0:38:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是想逼你做什麼\NWe're not making you do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.30,0:38:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我可以回家嗎\NThen can I just go back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.55,0:38:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-回芝加哥  -聽著  你緊張\N- Back to Chicago? - Listen, you have nerves,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.44,0:38:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可以理解\Nthat's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.27,0:38:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我他媽不想做了  好嗎\NI don't wanna fucking do it, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.12,0:38:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解你  沒關係\NI understand, it's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.52,0:38:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你要是現在退縮  梅根\NBut if you back out now, Megan...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.78,0:38:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不是為我  對吧\NThis isn't about me at all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.81,0:38:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我們會很不好  有損我們的形象\N...this is not good for us. It hurts us,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.28,0:38:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人覺得我們很鬆散\Nit makes us look unorganized.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.11,0:38:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這他媽是你亮相的機會\NThis is about your fucking moment to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.93,0:38:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不在乎我怎麼樣\NYou don't fucking care if do...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.56,0:38:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎  真心在乎\NI do care. I do care.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.23,0:38:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了我  也是為了你\NIt is about me and about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.31,0:38:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是為什麼\NAnd for whatever reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.59,0:38:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都說出了我們的經歷\Nwe both decided to share what happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.65,0:38:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們在乎  人們願意傾聽\NAnd it mattered and people listened
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.99,0:38:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們進去善始善終吧\Nso let's go in and finish what we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.59,0:38:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到  我不合適\NI can't, I'm not the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.63,0:38:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  梅根\NCome on, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.32,0:38:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我昨晚做了什麼嗎\NYou know what I did last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.96,0:38:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在酒吧裏找了個男的\NI picked up some guy at a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.43,0:38:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不認識他\NA total stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.86,0:38:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他在酒店裏瘋狂地干我\NI let him fuck my brains out at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.17,0:38:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前天晚上也是如此\NNight before, same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.39,0:38:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我停不下來\NI can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.19,0:38:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣我他媽才能...\NIt's my only way to fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.24,0:39:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天  真討厭這樣\NJesus, I fucking hate this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.12,0:39:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的手一抖我就...\Nwhen my hands shake like this and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.24,0:39:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\NIt's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.99,0:39:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沒事的  -我不是你想要的代言人\N- It's OK. - I'm not who you want to be your poster girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.93,0:39:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想的話就算了  不想就算了吧\NYou don't have to be. You don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.75,0:39:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我讓你失望了\NI'm sorry I'm letting you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.88,0:39:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  你沒讓我失望\NIt's OK, you're not letting me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.28,0:39:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了  沒事的\NIt's OK. It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.82,0:39:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候發表正式聲明\NWhen will it become official?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.28,0:39:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統今天下午就打電話\NPresident will make his call this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.40,0:39:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式批准將在明天上午宣佈\NOfficial approval will be announced in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.77,0:39:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協議內容沒有改動吧\NNo revisions to the agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.81,0:39:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  一切都寫在提案裏了\NNone. Everything is as spelled out in the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.92,0:39:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我會履行我的承諾\NThen I will uphold my end of the bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.02,0:39:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切斷資金流\NThe money will be cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.98,0:39:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說要證明  現在我們也要\NYou required proof. Now we want some.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.15,0:39:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼證明\NWhat sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.64,0:39:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的誠意\NOf your commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.10,0:39:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終止和塔斯克的合資項目\NYou kill your co-venture with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.84,0:39:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們當初可沒說到這個\NThat was never part of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.37,0:39:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在說了\NIt is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.84,0:39:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貿易戰持續的話  精煉廠的事也成不了\NThe refinery can't proceed while we're in a trade war.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.95,0:39:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要你徹底取消跟他的合作\NWe want you to kill it for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.85,0:39:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且今天就辦\NAnd we want you to kill it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.75,0:39:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給塔斯克打電話吧\NMake the call to Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.37,0:40:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是上班時間  要說公事嗎\NIt's business hours. Is this a business call?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.73,0:40:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.55,0:40:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望不是公事\NI was hoping it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.42,0:40:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚有什麼安排嗎\NWhat are you doing tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.59,0:40:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上要上飛機了\NJust about to get on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.47,0:40:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裏去\NWhere to?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.38,0:40:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了分清界限嗎\NBoundaries, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.74,0:40:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公事才有界限\NWork related.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.82,0:40:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是去度假\NI don't take vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.07,0:40:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候回來呢\NCan you tell me when you'll be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.63,0:40:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天  很快就回來\NTomorrow. It's a quick trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.97,0:40:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想和我共進晚餐嗎\NDo you want to have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.48,0:40:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\NI'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.77,0:40:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶上你的行李吧\NBring your carry-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.65,0:40:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完飯順便過夜\NYou can stay over after.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.76,0:40:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.69,0:40:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有空嗎\NDo you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.60,0:40:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有\NAbsolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.66,0:40:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統一個小時前接受了我的辭呈\NThe president accepted my resignation an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.03,0:41:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NYes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.11,0:41:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差點說我改變心意了\NI almost told him that I changed my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.98,0:41:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我意識到沒有挽回餘地了\Nbut I realized it wouldn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.91,0:41:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣\NFor whatever it's worth,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.88,0:41:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提到了你的忠誠\NI did bring up your loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.18,0:41:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及你出色的工作\Nand how good you are at your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.76,0:41:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他並不需要我的提醒\NNot that he needed me to remind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.42,0:41:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你舉薦了我  我會一直心懷感激\NAnd I will always be grateful you recommended me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.12,0:41:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段路很精彩\NIt has been quite a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.81,0:41:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然比我想的短了一點\NShorter than I would've hoped,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.14,0:41:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還有大好前途等著我呢\Nbut I have a long career ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.76,0:41:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了\NNo doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.07,0:41:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告訴你\NAnd just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.00,0:41:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想造成任何輿論風波\NI don't plan on making any fuss in the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.56,0:41:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人問  我一定都是溢美之辭\NYou'll hear nothing but my praises if I'm asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.52,0:41:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有樣東西要給你\NI have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.80,0:41:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾星期前\NA few weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.53,0:41:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統跟我說起在你家的那頓晚飯\Nthe president told me about a dinner he had at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.19,0:41:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不停地說你的內戰模型\NHe went on and on about your Civil War models.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.70,0:41:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說跟你一起給玩具士兵上色可開心了\NHow much fun he had painting the toy soldiers with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是史密森尼的主管給我的\NThis was given to me by the director of the Smithsonian.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}位於美國華盛頓的一系列博物館和研究機構的集合組織
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.36,0:41:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是第一枚授予美籍西班牙人的榮譽勳章\NIt's the first Medal of Honor awarded to a Hispanic-American.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.72,0:41:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是授予約瑟夫·德·卡斯特羅下士的\NCorporal Joseph De Castro.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.56,0:41:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為聯軍作戰\NHe fought for the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.65,0:41:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達  我不知道該說什麼好\NLinda, I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.37,0:41:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很顯然總統把你當朋友看\NIt's clear the president sees you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.80,0:41:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒把我當過朋友\NI've never been that to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.01,0:41:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的工作超過友誼\NBut his job is bigger than friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.62,0:42:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我們倆都要重要\NIt's bigger than you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.39,0:42:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能好好輔佐他  彌補我的遺憾\NI just hope you'll look out for him the way I've tried to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.78,0:42:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.06,0:42:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會好好珍惜這枚勳章\NAnd I'll treasure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.24,0:42:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見  副總統先生\NGoodbye, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.82,0:42:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從未像此刻這樣尊敬她\NI've never thought higher of her than I do at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.45,0:42:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她輸了  但她拼盡全力了\NShe lost, but she played to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.79,0:42:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德買通馮了\NUnderwood got to Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.91,0:42:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精煉廠沒戲了\NThe refinery's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.28,0:42:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷森耍了我們\NGrayson played us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.79,0:42:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們別無選擇\NWe're running outta options.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.92,0:42:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想  珍\NWhat do you think, Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.47,0:42:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他的\NFuck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.71,0:42:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動手\NDo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.45,0:43:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.13,0:43:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫我們  桑德拉\NThank you for doing this, Sandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.84,0:43:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德\NRichard.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.83,0:43:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好嗎  理查德\NHow are you, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.55,0:43:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的情況時好時壞\NHe has his good days and his bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.52,0:43:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天還不錯\NThis is a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.97,0:43:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他希望在你們結束後能和你聊聊\NHe'd love to spend a few minutes with you after your meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.35,0:43:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.69,0:43:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧師在裏面\NThe reverend's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.86,0:43:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃剋夫人\NMrs. Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.85,0:43:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.70,0:43:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\NMr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.19,0:43:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧師\NReverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.86,0:43:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可以效勞\NHow can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.03,0:44:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得在這屋裏裝個電扇  弗蘭西斯\NYou need to get a fan in here, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.44,0:44:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空調已經在全速運轉了\NWell, the AC is all the way up to full blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.04,0:44:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說膠水的味道\NI mean from the fumes, the glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.79,0:44:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是樂趣的一部分嘛\NOh, that's half the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.67,0:44:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根·漢納希今天臨陣退縮了\NMegan Hennessy bailed on us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.46,0:44:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.07,0:44:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她太緊張了\NHer nerves got to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.70,0:44:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她決定不在公眾面前露面\NAnd she decided she didn't want to be in the public eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.62,0:44:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也可以理解\NWell, we can sympathize with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.20,0:44:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格的電話\NThat was Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.38,0:44:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.67,0:44:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯\NSeth.
